  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Your mastery makes the most of your armor.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Armor Focus, base attack bonus +6, proficiency with selected armor.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>The armor check penalty of the selected armor decreases by 1 (to a minimum of 0). You also use your character level in place of your base attack bonus for the purpose of armor mastery feat prerequisites.<br/><br/><b>Special</b><br/>You can gain this feat multiple times. Its effects do not stack. Each time you take the feat, it applies to a new type of armor.<br/><br/><b>Combat Trick</b><br/>You can spend 5 stamina points to negate your armor's armor check penalty for 1 skill check. (See page 16.)",
